      "patch": "@@ -0,0 +1,11 @@\n+---\n+description: \"Accept a positional argument that is declared as secret\"\n+args:\n+  positional:\n+    - name: value\n+      type: secret\n+      description: \"Must be a secret expression\"\n+---\n+\n+operator = \"typed_positional_secret\"\n+value = $value"
